    <item>
      <title>南非城镇欠水务局 12 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/south-african-towns-owe-water-boards-1-2-billion-bus-day-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《商业日报》援引水利与卫生部长佩米·马约迪纳的话称，南非 15 个水务局共欠下各市政府 213 亿兰特（12 亿美元）的债务，这些债务威胁到这些水务局的财务生存能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/south-african-towns-owe-water-boards-1-2-billion-bus-day-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 07:00:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
