    <item>
      <title>大学称澳大利亚限制留学生人数造成损害</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/australia-s-cap-on-overseas-students-damaging-universities-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚各大学警告称，如果政府过快限制国际学生人数，将会导致大量失业，一家行业机构称，这项拟议政策是前所未有的“部长越权行为”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/australia-s-cap-on-overseas-students-damaging-universities-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 03:58:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯赢得民主党提名，巩固与特朗普的对决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/harris-clinches-democratic-nomination-cementing-trump-matchup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 获得民主党总统候选人提名，在一场网络唱名投票中获胜，成为第一位领导美国主要政党总统候选人的黑人女性和亚裔美国人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/harris-clinches-democratic-nomination-cementing-trump-matchup</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 03:50:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国解除宵禁，军队准备组建政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/bangladesh-president-vows-to-hold-election-as-soon-as-possible</link>
      <description><![CDATA[长期领导人谢赫·哈西娜被推翻后，孟加拉国当局解除了为期一周的宵禁，该国正在等待由军方支持的新临时政府的成立。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/bangladesh-president-vows-to-hold-election-as-soon-as-possible</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 00:56:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行因市场崩盘后加息时机遭批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/boj-under-fire-for-rate-hike-timing-after-japan-market-meltdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行上周的货币政策紧缩措施引发了一波批评，因为这似乎引发了日本股市的历史性暴跌，并加剧了全球市场动荡 —— 有可能使任何进一步加息的计划被搁置。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/boj-under-fire-for-rate-hike-timing-after-japan-market-meltdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 13:37:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
